data.description: Looking for a semi-custom 2-story home located in an upscale Golf Course Community, The Links?Well you've found it here! The modern eat-in kitchen features white cabinets, counter space galore, large island and pantry.The open concept living room has a stone accented gas fireplace with vaulted ceilings. Wood shutters throughout just add to the exquisite touches of this gorgeous home! The massive master bedroom and master bathroom is truly a sanctuary, you definitely will fall in love. This home also boasts 3 bedrooms with all the possibilities of having 4 while including a large flex room and den area that leaves nothing else to be desired.  Your spacious 3 car garage will fit all those toys that you enjoy. Beauty in every corner is truly what you'll find in this gem.
